'''刺蛾科'''（学名：Limacodidae）是[[昆虫纲|昆虫纲]][[鳞翅目|鳞翅目]][[双孔亚目|双孔亚目]][[斑蛾总科|斑蛾总科]]下的一个[[科|科]]<ref name="biods.2019132">{{cite journal |last1=Meng |first1=Jiao |last2=Jing |first2=Li |last3=Huifeng |first3=Zhao |last4=Chunsheng |first4=Wu |last5=Aibing |first5=Zhang |title=Species diversity and global distribution of Limacodidae (Lepidoptera) using online databases |journal=Biodiversity Science |date=2019-07-20 |volume=27 |issue=7 |pages=778 |doi=10.17520/biods.2019132}}</ref>。已记录的种数达301属1,672种<ref>{{cite journal |author1=van Nieukerken EJ |coauthors=Kaila L, Kitching J, Kristensen NP, Lees DC, Minet J, Mitter C, Mutanen M, Regier JC, Simonsen TJ, Wahlberg N, Yen SH, Zahiri R, Adamski D, Baixeras J, Bartsch D, Bengtsson BÅ, Brown JW, Bucheli SR, Davis DR, Prins JD, Prins WD, Epstein ME, Gentili-Poole P, Gielis C, Hättenschwiler P, Hausmann A, Holloway JD, Kallies A, Karsholt O, Kawahara AY, Koster S, Kozlov MV, Lafontaine JD, Lamas G, Landry JF, Lee S, Nuss M, Park KT, Penz C, Rota J, Schintlmeister A, Schmidt BC, Sohn JC, Solis MA, Tarmann GM, Warren AD, Weller S, Yakovlev RV, Zolotuhin VV, Zwick A |title=Animal Biodiversity: An outline of higher classification and survey of taxonomic richness |journal=Zootaxa |date=2011 |volume=314 |pages=212–221 |url=https://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/2011/f/zt03148p221.pdf |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031090659/https://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/2011/f/zt03148p221.pdf |access-date=2020-11-19 |archive-date=2020-10-31 |language=en }}</ref>。

刺蛾成虫身体和前翅密生绒毛和厚鳞。幼虫体扁，大部分种类体表生有枝刺和[[螫毛|螫毛]]。当人被刺蛾幼虫蜇过后, [[皮肤|皮肤]]会[[红肿|红肿]]、[[疼痛|疼痛]]，严重甚至会威胁生命。因此刺蛾科幼虫被称为“'''痒辣子'''”、“'''火辣子'''”或“'''刺毛虫'''”<ref name="武春生">{{cite journal |author1=武春生 |title=中国刺蛾科幼虫的寄主植物多样性分析 |journal=《[[森林病虫|森林病虫]]》 |date=2010 |issue=2 |pages=1-4 |url=http://www.cqvip.com/qk/92651a/201002/33175773.html |access-date=2020-11-19 |language=zh-hans }}</ref>。

幼虫多以阔叶树叶为食。是重要经济林、行道林的主要[[害虫|害虫]]<ref name="武春生" />。

[[金蛾科|金蛾科]]（[[Chrysopolomidae|Chrysopolomidae]]）原來跟刺蛾科一樣是斑蛾总科之下的一個科，由兩個亞科組成，包含約30個分佈於非洲的物種<ref>{{cite book |chapter-url=https://link.springer.com/referenceworkentry/10.1007%2F0-306-48380-7_88 |chapter=African Slug Caterpillar Moths (Lepidoptera: Chrysopolomidae) |first=John B. |last=Heppner |title=Encyclopedia of Entomology |edition=2005 Edition |doi=10.1007/0-306-48380-7_88 |language=en |access-date=2021-09-05 |archive-date=2018-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180608162457/https://link.springer.com/referenceworkentry/10.1007%2F0-306-48380-7_88 }}</ref>，在較新的文獻，這個科被降格，成為了本科之下的一個亞科[[金蛾亞科|金蛾亞科]]（[[Chrysopolominae|Chrysopolominae]]），原來在金蛾科之下的兩個亞科現在變成了金蛾亞科的異名<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.afromoths.net/subfamilies/show/420020 |title=Chrysopolominae Aurivillius, 1895 (subfamily) |work=Afromoths.net |access-date=2021-09-06 |language=en |archive-date=2021-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210906173747/http://www.afromoths.net/subfamilies/show/420020 }}</ref>。

